data.description: This is a quality craftsman styled Northridge home with engineered hand planed wood floors, custom doors, full window wraps, knotty maple custom cabinets, chiseled edge granite counters, large great room/dining area, breakfast bar,pantry,vaulted ceilings,crown molding, high end SS appliances and walk in closet. The garage has built in counters/shelving along with a brand new shed with shelving, windows and a new patio area and cabana! Great location near shopping, Asante Three Rivers medical center, schools, parks and the great outdoors of Josephine County with the Rogue, Applegate and Illinois River! VA assumable loan at 2.75% interest!!
